commits.author: Mark Robert Miller
commits.sourceNew:
/** * Performs a rollback of all non-committed documents pending. *

* Note that this is not a true rollback as in databases. Content you have * previously added may have already been committed due to autoCommit, buffer * full, other client performing a commit etc. So this is only a best-effort * rollback. * * @throws IOException * If there is a low-level I/O error. */ public UpdateResponse rollbackTransaction() throws IOException, SolrServerException;
